    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Hi @algobot are you open source? :)\r\n\r\n@zeke As @Haroenv said, you can get this for you just by:\r\n- having a docs build command\r\n- linking your GitHub projects to a Netlify account\r\n- Creating a GitHub user that will be the user posting comments from Netlify (the one having the token)\r\n\r\nThat's it!",
